## 1. OLTP vs OLAP

| Feature            | OLTP (Online Transaction Processing) | OLAP (Online Analytical Processing) |
|--------------------|---------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| **Purpose**        | Day-to-day transactions               | Data analysis & reporting            |
| **Operations**     | CRUD (Insert, Update, Delete, Read)   | Aggregations, Summaries, Complex Queries |
| **Data Type**      | Current, real-time data               | Historical data                      |
| **Query Speed**    | Fast for small transactions           | Fast for large read queries          |
| **Design**         | Normalized (to avoid redundancy)      | Denormalized (Star/Snowflake schema) |
| **Users**          | Clerks, Customers, End-users          | Analysts, Data Scientists, Managers  |
| **Examples**       | Banking, E-commerce, Ticket Booking   | Sales reports, BI dashboards         |
